com.itko.lisa.remote.transactions.interceptors

Interface IInterceptor

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    AbstractInterceptor

    public interface IInterceptor
    IInterceptors provides some hooks that get invoked by the TransactionDispatcher to execute some extra logic. IMPORTANT NOTE: don't put anything in interceptor static initializers unless you know what you're doing!!! User: jd Date: Jun 29, 2007 11:31:03 AM
